label: Arm
description: A group or subgroup of participants in a clinical trial that receives a specific intervention/treatment, or no intervention, according to the trial's protocol.

label: Clinical Protocol
description: Clinical Protocol part of a Clinical Study

label: Condition
description: The Condition under investigation in the respective Protocol/Study.

label: Facility
description: Facility participating in a Clinical Protocol

label: Medicinal Product
description: The Medicinal Product under investigation in the respective Protocol/Study.

label: Person
description: The Persons involved in the Protocol/Study.
